jalse.entities

Class DefaultEntityProxyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.entities.DefaultEntityProxyFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityProxyFactory

    public class DefaultEntityProxyFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntityProxyFactory
    This is the default EntityProxyFactory implementation for JALSE. This proxy factory will use EntityFunctionResolver to resolve an EntityFunction to translate the proxy Method calls to EntityMethods. Override addResolverFunctions() to change what EntityMethodFunctions are added to the resolver.

    NOTE: Proxies are cached per Entity using DefaultEntityProxyFactory.EntityProxyCache.
    See Also:
    uncacheProxyOfEntity(Entity, Class), uncacheProxiesOfEntity(Entity), uncacheAllProxies()
